{"tid":1980224,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"紐約期油價格續挫 跌破每桶15美元","createTime":"2020-04-20T03:02:57.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-20T12:48:24.000Z","uid":141151,"like":12,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":29,"replies":[{"pid":"b77e62c289ff9caf5dc83e1159aa9af7964dc904","tid":1980224,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-20T03:02:57.000Z","msg":"紐約期油價格續挫 跌破每桶15美元<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://ec.ltn.com.tw/article/breakingnews/3139152\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fec.ltn.com.tw%2Farticle%2Fbreakingnews%2F3139152&d=Sy1M3c%2BVV8kZ1V6TqBoGPv8K46P7%2BXxs1F7ZCKkfkQw%3D&h=a413e525\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fec.ltn.com.tw%2Farticle%2Fbreakingnews%2F3139152&h=1b79a44f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://ec.ltn.com.tw/article/breakingnews/3139152</a><br />\n<br />\n〔財經頻道／綜合報導〕在市場仍持續憂慮武漢肺炎疫情將嚴重削弱原油需求，並擔心美國儲油設施恐將達到極限的背景下，使得國際油價延續上周五跌勢，今早於亞洲交易時段進一步下跌。紐約西德州中級原油5月交割價今早開市一度重挫逾20%，每桶跌破15美元。<br />\n<br />\n綜合媒體報導，紐約西德州中級原油5月交割價今早在亞洲電子交易時段不久後，一度重挫20.8%，低見14.47美元，續刷1999年以來新低。目前最新報價仍跌14.41%，報15.78美元。<br />\n<br />\n而布蘭特原油6月交割價，則跌2.47%，報27.64美元。"},{"pid":"31b2bd7500f3e46ebf9dc39eadfb4111644241e8","tid":1980224,"uid":199957,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-20T05:02:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"29b23552d68eaadf918f2d5723d5589ee4e9bf66","tid":1980224,"uid":154647,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-20T05:05:46.000Z","msg":"連登好多傻西買左油<br />\n<br />\n信我 會去到十蚊"},{"pid":"6954bcb9ab66f69242b54d8fde9f13b786ed21b1","tid":1980224,"uid":60529,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-20T05:08:16.000Z","msg":"期貨轉倉"},{"pid":"8b66cebaa399553d012c7adeb14f462f2b724c63","tid":1980224,"uid":259777,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-20T05:08:37.000Z","msg":"就嚟石油平過可樂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n再過兩星期可能加